      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,15 @@\n+---\n+title: \"Gadget Pattern\"\n+type: concept\n+tags: [concept, pattern, engineering]\n+status: reference\n+related: [\"[[Concepts/Widget Theory]]\"]\n+---\n+\n+# Gadget Pattern\n+\n+A design pattern derived from [[Widget Theory]] for building resilient components.\n+\n+## Usage\n+Applied in [[Acme Project]] to handle failure scenarios.\n+The pattern was validated by [[Alice Smith]]'s team."
