      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,21 @@\n+---\n+title: \"Widget Theory\"\n+aliases: [\"Widget Framework\", \"WT\"]\n+type: concept\n+tags: [concept, framework, engineering]\n+status: reference\n+related: [\"[[Concepts/Gadget Pattern]]\"]\n+---\n+\n+# Widget Theory\n+\n+A theoretical framework for understanding component interactions in complex systems.\n+Originally proposed by [[Alice Smith]] and refined through collaboration with [[Bob Jones]].\n+\n+## Key Properties\n+- Composable: widgets can be nested arbitrarily\n+- Observable: state changes propagate predictably\n+- Related to [[Gadget Pattern]] as a practical application\n+\n+## Applications\n+See [[Acme Project]] for a production implementation."
