      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,18 @@\n+---\n+title: \"Acme Project\"\n+type: idea\n+status: active\n+tags: [idea, project]\n+first_mentioned: 2025-06-15\n+---\n+\n+# Acme Project\n+\n+## What\n+A production system implementing [[Gadget Pattern]] principles derived from [[Widget Theory]].\n+\n+## Status\n+Currently in development. [[Alice Smith]] leads the implementation.\n+\n+## Related\n+- [[Nonexistent Page]] \u2014 this link tests stub node handling"
