      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,18 @@\n+---\n+title: Alice Smith\n+tags: [person, engineer]\n+aliases: [\"A. Smith\"]\n+type: person\n+status: active\n+---\n+\n+# Alice Smith\n+\n+## Context\n+- Lead engineer on the [[Widget Theory]] project\n+- Collaborates with [[Bob Jones]] on research\n+- Proposed the [[Acme Project]] as a way to test [[Gadget Pattern]] in production\n+\n+## Notes\n+Alice presented at the 2025 conference about emergent patterns in distributed systems.\n+She argued that [[Widget Theory]] provides a better framework than traditional approaches."
